      1          /**
      2           *  @file
      3           *  @defgroup   CLASS_B
      4           *
      5           *  @brief      The Atod GDM for STM32G0x is a module that implements the
      6           *              Atod standard API (Application Programming interface for the Atod module) for the STM32G0x family
      7           *              of microcontrollers. This module provides the interface to the application to read the Digital value
      8           *              from the Analog signal using ADC Engine.
      9           *  @details    In addition to regular Atod GDM module, Atod contains all necessary mechanisms to Ensure fully safe
     10           *              reading of digital values from the analog signal and
     11           *              meets requirements from Normative IEC 60730-1 (annex H.11).
     12           *
     13           *              The STM32G0x implements up to 18 A/D channels. It has 16 External channels and 3 internal channels
     14           *              ATOD_CH12, ATOD_CH13 & ATOD_CH14 are used as internal channels.
     15           * <pre>
     16           *               Following table contains the ADC Channel, Port, Pin associated with ADC module for STM32F0x
     17           *                --------------------------------------
     18           *               | ATOD Channel   |  Port    |   Pin    |
     19           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     20           *               |    ATOD_CH0    |   PORTA  |    0     |
     21           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     22           *               |    ATOD_CH1    |   PORTA  |    1     |
     23           *               | ---------------|----------|----------|
     24           *               |    ATOD_CH2    |   PORTA  |    2     |
     25           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     26           *               |    ATOD_CH3    |   PORTA  |    3     |
     27           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     28           *               |    ATOD_CH4    |   PORTA  |    4     |
     29           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     30           *               |    ATOD_CH5    |   PORTA  |    5     |
     31           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     32           *               |    ATOD_CH6    |   PORTA  |    6     |
     33           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     34           *               |    ATOD_CH7    |   PORTA  |    7     |
     35           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     36           *               |    ATOD_CH8    |   PORTB  |    0     |
     37           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     38           *               |    ATOD_CH9    |   PORTB  |    1     |
     39           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     40           *               |    ATOD_CH10   |   PORTB  |    2     |
     41           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     42           *               |    ATOD_CH11   |   PORTB  |    10    |
     43           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     44           *               |    ATOD_CH12   |  Internal Channel   |
     45           *               |                | (Temperature Sensor)|
     46           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     47           *               |    ATOD_CH13   |  Internal Channel   |
     48           *               |                |     (Vrefint)       |
     49           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     50           *               |    ATOD_CH14   |  Monitoring Vbat    |
     51           *               |                |     (Vbat/3)        |
     52           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     53           *               |    ATOD_CH15   |   PORTB  |    11    |
     54           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     55           *               |    ATOD_CH16   |   PORTB  |    12    |
     56           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     57           *               |    ATOD_CH17   |   PORTC  |    4     |
     58           *               |----------------|----------|----------|
     59           *               |    ATOD_CH18   |   PORTC  |    5     |
     60           *                -------------------------------------- </pre>
